title.narrative: OUTP 1.6: HEALTH SYSTEMS STRENGTHENING

description.narrative: Output 1.6: National Health Systems strengthened., which contributes to Child Health, Health Systems Strengthening. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Outcome 1: Pregnant women and children of less than five years of age have access to quality maternal new-born and child health services nationally, by 2015.
